title: Google\Cloud\Bigtable\Admin\V2\AppProfile_MultiClusterRoutingUseAny
name: AppProfile_MultiClusterRoutingUseAny
description:
Read/write requests may be routed to any cluster in the instance, and will fail over to another cluster in the event of transient errors or delays.

Choosing this option sacrifices read-your-writes consistency to improve availability.
